Day 12: Feeling great. Been bodyache and headache free for 3 days now 🙌🏾. Still no smell or taste but I’ll take that! Had a virtual appointment w/ my doctor and was cleared. Cleaning & sanitizing for baby girl to come home on Sunday! 🙏🏾
